					<p id='intelliTxt'>I recently had a cold with a nagging cough and sore throat. My sis sent me the recipe to a natural cough suppressant that I could make at home. I honestly didnt think it would work, but since I had all the ingredients on hand I gave it a try. I found out...it really does work!! It suppressed my cough and soothed my sore throat, with no medicinal side effects. I have a friend that calls it &quot;the cough syrup of the gods&quot;. Here are the steps to making the best homemade cough suppressant.<span></span></p>
					<!-- google_ad_section_end() -->
